quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  19,66,"Munthu amati, “Pamene ine nditafa kodi ndidzaukitsidwa ndi kukhalanso ndi moyo?”"
  19,67,Kodi munthu sakumbukira kuti tidamulenga iye pamene poyamba sadali chinthu china chilichonse
  19,68,Motero pali Ambuye wako; ndithudi Tidzawasonkhanitsa pamodzi ndi a Satana ndipo onse tidzawabweretsa m’mphepete mwa Gahena atagwada
  19,69,Ndipo mwachoonadi tidzachotsa mugulu lililonse onse amene adanyoza Mulungu kwambiri
  19,70,Ndithudi Ife tilikuwadziwa kwambiri amene ali oyenera kuotchedwa
  19,71,Palibe wina wa inu amene sadzapita kumbali ya Moto. Limeneli ndilo lamulo la mphamvu la Ambuye wanu
  19,72,"Ndipo Ife tidzapulumutsa onse amene amaopa ndi kuwasiya ochita zoipa, atagwada, kuti amve ululu wake"
  19,73,"Pamene zivumbulutso zathu zilakatulidwa momveka kwa iwo, anthu osakhulupirira amanena kwa anthu okhulupirira kuti, “Kodi ndi gulu liti pa magulu awiriwa limene lili ndi malo abwino okhala ndi anthu apamwamba?”"
  19,74,"Kodi ndi mibadwo ingati yakale imene tidaononga iwo asanadze, mibadwo imene idali ndi zinthu zabwino ndiponso zokongola"
  19,75,"Nena, “Aliyense amene alakwa, Mwini chisoni chosatha adzawaonjezera nthawi, mpaka pamene adzaone zomwe adalonjezedwa. Kaya ndi chilango kapena ola lomaliza, pamenepo ndiye adzadziwa kuti ndani amene ali mwini wa malo oipa ndi gulu lankhondo lofoka.”"
  19,76,Mulungu amapitiriza kutsogolera iwo amene atsatira njira yoyenera. Ntchito zabwino zimene zili ndi malipiro osatha zili ndi mphotho yabwino pamaso pa Ambuye wako ndiponso zotsatira zake ndi zabwino
  19,77,"Kodi mwamuona munthu amene akana zivumbulutso zathu ndipo amanena kuti, “Ine, ndithudi, ndidzapatsidwa chuma ndi ana?”"
  19,78,Kodi iye waziona zinthu zosaoneka kapena Mwini chisoni chosatha wamupatsa lonjezo lotere
  19,79,Osatheka! Ife tidzalemba zimene akunena ndi kuchipanga chilango chake kukhala chachitali
  19,80,Zonse zimene azilankhula iye zidzabwerera kwa Ife ndipo adzadza pamaso pathu yekha
  19,81,Anthu osakhulupirira adadzisankhira milungu ina kuti iwapatse mphamvu ndi ulemerero
  19,82,Ayi. Koma milunguyo idzakana kupembedza kwawo ndipo idzakhala adani awo